commit.message:
Remove libgcjdata hack.   Fix jv-scan usage in dejagnu.

From-SVN: r42812

@@ -1,3 +1,12 @@
+2001-06-02  Anthony Green  <green@redhat.com>
+
+	* configure: Rebuild.
+	* configure.in: Remove data_start hack.
+	* libgcj.spec.in: Ditto.
+	* Makefile.in: Rebuild.
+	* Makefile.am: Ditto.
+	* libgcjdata.c: Remove.
+	
 2001-06-02  Anthony Green  <green@redhat.com>
 
 	* configure: Rebuild.
